<p class="paragraph-text">This particular performance, recorded in December 2012, was conducted by Yutaka Sado – a Japanese conductor who studied under <a href="/composers/bernstein-l/">Leonard Bernstein</a> and <a href="/artists/seiji-ozawa/">Seiji Ozawa</a>.</p>
